{
  "description_cn": "<p>圆形包装，尺寸来自图像颜色。</p><p>对图像进行布点采样，根据采样点的灰度值生成大小不同的圆（灰度值映射到指定的半径范围），圆之间进行碰撞模拟。</p>",
  "description_en": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Circle packing with sizes from image colours。</span></p><p>The image is sampled at points, and circles of different sizes are generated based on the gray values ​​of the sampled points (the gray values ​​are mapped to a specified radius range). Collision simulation is performed between the circles.</p>",
  "images": [
    "ImageCircles.png",
    "ImageCircles.gif"
  ],
  "video": "",
  "tags": [
    "线"
  ],
  "parameters": [
    {
      "name": "Pts",
      "cn": "圆心",
      "en": "Points",
      "default": "Null，点",
      "desc_cn": "初始圆心位置",
      "desc_en": "Initial circle centre locations"
    },
    {
      "name": "M",
      "cn": "网格",
      "en": "Mesh",
      "default": "Null，网格",
      "desc_cn": "彩色网格-较暗的区域会出现较小的圆圈",
      "desc_en": "Coloured mesh - darker areas will get smaller circles"
    },
    {
      "name": "Min",
      "cn": "最小半径",
      "en": "Min",
      "default": "0.2，数字",
      "desc_cn": "最小圆半径",
      "desc_en": "Smallest circle radius"
    },
    {
      "name": "Max",
      "cn": "最大半径",
      "en": "Max",
      "default": "1，数字",
      "desc_cn": "最大圆半径",
      "desc_en": "Largest circle radius"
    },
    {
      "name": "Crvs",
      "cn": "曲线",
      "en": "Curves",
      "default": "Null，曲线",
      "desc_cn": "可选碰撞曲线",
      "desc_en": "Optional collision curves"
    },
    {
      "name": "Strength",
      "cn": "强度",
      "en": "Strength",
      "default": "1，数字",
      "desc_cn": "强度",
      "desc_en": "Strength"
    }
  ],
  "outputs": [
    {
      "name": "I",
      "cn": "图像圆",
      "en": "ImageCircles",
      "default": "Null",
      "desc_cn": "生成的图像圆",
      "desc_en": "ImageCircles Goal"
    }
  ],
  "examples": [
